19      +6  +2      7       3/2     6
20      +6  +2      8       3/2     6

  
Armor: Any  

Weapons: Clerics get 1 Primary Weapon and 3 Secondary Weapons. Their primary weapon does 1d8 damage. Secondary weapons do 1d6.  Untrained weapons do 1d4 damage.

Combat Stunts: Clerics start with no combat stunts.  They get new Combat Stunts at levels  6, 12 and 18.

Domains: Clerics get powers called Prayers from their deities based on Domains. Domains are areas in which certain deities hold sway. Each Domain has 5 Prayers: 2 Tier 1 Prayers, 2 Tier 2 Prayers and a single Tier 3 Prayer. When a cleric chooses a Domain for the first time, he gets the Tier 1 Prayers. When he chooses it a second time he gets the Tier 2 Prayers as well. A third choosing gets him the Tier 3 Prayer.
  

  

</rich_text>
