				<rich_text>Levitate
Casting Time: 1 Action  
Range: 25 ft  
Target: You or 1 creature / object within range. 
Duration: 1 minute

Levitate allows you to move yourself, another creature, or an object up and down as you wish. A creature must be willing to be levitated, and an object must be unattended or possessed by a willing creature. You can mentally direct the recipient to move up or down as much as 20 feet each round; doing so as your movement in the Movement phase of combat. You cannot move the recipient horizontally, but the recipient could clamber along the face of a cliff, for example, or push against a ceiling to move laterally. 

Max weight of the object being levitated is 100 pounds.
  
Augmentation: +1 minute per Mana; +100 pounds per Mana
</rich_text>
